<p>You are <%= @ticket.report_type_pretty %> <%= link_to_user(@ticket.model) %>.</p>

<% case @ticket.report_type %>
<% when "report" %>
  Tell us what they've done wrong. Ensure you provide proof, especially for accusations such as being underage.<br>
  If you meant to make a commendation instead, click <%= link_to("here", model_new_ticket_path(model: @ticket.model, report_type: "commendation")) %>.
<% when "commendation" %>
  Tell us what great things they've done for the site.<br>
  If you meant to file a report instead, click <%= link_to("here", model_new_ticket_path(model: @ticket.model, report_type: "report")) %>.
<% end %>
